        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="45" name="Message" rows="6" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
Well not today actually, I bound myself the day before at North wall after one guild cleared it. Then logged on the next morning when the whole place respawned. I didn't really think I could do as well as I thought but I started pulling carefully and would root dot right at north wall.
[img]http://home.pacbell.net/odessit2/folder/fear01.jpg[/img]

I learned that scarelings are a bitch, and I had to kill quite a few of them this way before I could pull the good stuff.

Eventually I killed apes and a few spiders. Even got nice nice monk leggings =p
[img]http://home.pacbell.net/odessit2/folder/fear07.jpg[/img]

After I had north wall cleared up a bit I decided to fear kite a little.
[img]http://home.pacbell.net/odessit2/folder/fear05.jpg[/img]

[img]http://home.pacbell.net/odessit2/folder/fear06.jpg[/img]

[img]http://home.pacbell.net/odessit2/folder/fear08.jpg[/img]

It was fun fear kiting in PoF the fear pathing is great. The hardest part was pulling stuff, it required a lot of well timed FD's and rooting. In fact we sometimes do it better than monks because we can root something, FD and let it's friend leave.

[img]http://home.pacbell.net/odessit2/folder/fear09.jpg[/img]

Thanks to the ducky I was able to root dot 2 things at a time hehe. /hug epic.

Pretty soon I couldn't believe how far I cleared into fear. So I decided to see how far I can get. I soon started pulling the TT bridge area and even got to use charm :)

[img]http://home.pacbell.net/odessit2/folder/fear02.jpg[/img]

And finally reached west wall with my charmed buddy, I was gonna pull boogies but I was pretty tired by this time and had a guild raid to go to.

[img]http://home.pacbell.net/odessit2/folder/fear10.jpg[/img]

This was probably one of the best things I have done in eq. Very fun and challenging to do at 60. And got a lot of nice research components, gems, and even a cleric belt.

Next time I wanna see if I can go even further and maybe pull boogies, I want a blighted robe dammit >:-|

NECRO > ALL

