bly one of the best things I have done in eq. Very fun and challenging to do at 60. And got a lot of nice research components, gems, and even a cleric belt.</P><P>Next time I wanna see if I can go even further and maybe pull boogies, I want a blighted robe dammit >:-|</P><P>NECRO > ALL</P><P>Edited by - Xell Naga on 08/03/2001  21:37:12</P><P>Edited by - Xell Naga on 08/03/2001  21:46:45</font></td>
