ed quickly return home. then I stand and run to group, now here's why ghetto engulfing:  It doesnt last very long.  This tactic doesnt always work and sometimes they still return together.  This really sucks when you have dooming on cause you have to wait a long ass time for it to wear off, group gets ancy, and so on.  It also has half the cast time, half the mana, and still drops things slower than you are.</P><P>God I wish I had my epic, me and a cleric buddy would be in hate every night.</P><P>-Zondro Devilldoll 57 Gnecro of Karana<BR>(VERY BAD)</font></td>
