ll would have been wiped and doing a nice little CR after all was said and done.  </P><P>That encounter, I will never forget, and is what actually pursuaded me to continue playing my Necro from here on out.  I'm always welcome on raids, and I'm always useful.  Can't as for anything more.. Can I??</P><P><BR>Arathon Windmiller<BR>News Hound - Necro.EQClasses<BR>Gnome Necro - Drinal<BR></font></td>
